Humans of HOKA: Ahmed Muhumed ✨

“That responsibility for me is to ensure while I have this opportunity, while I can give back, I should give back, so in 10-15 years’ time, when my running career is over, I can say I did not only make it for myself, I tried to have as much impact as I could along the way.” - @ahmedmuhumed14 

In our latest #HumansOfHOKA film, HOKA athlete Ahmed Muhumed takes us on a journey through his childhood, his running motivations, and–most recently–hosting a youth running event in the Somali Region of Ethiopia where he grew up. 

Watch the full film at the link in bio. 🔗🎥
